    {
      "text": "聖闘士星矢をベースにしたアクションRPG。アルゴスの戦士として戦う。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "An open-world action-adventure game for the Nintendo Entertainment System that features a barbarian warrior with a distinctive \"diskarmor\" weapon. It is distinct from the original 1986 Arcade game Rygar, which saw numerous home console ports.",
